{"tid":92714,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜聊天室","createTime":"2017-01-23T19:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T21:12:55.000Z","uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd81eca0ccef84296ec694eeb29d3a114e2804a","tid":92714,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:40:55.000Z","msg":"好唔開心。<br />\n上年gpa仲有3.3，今年無心機走好多堂，結果gpa得1.6，cgpa得翻2.7，我唔要求first class hon，但second up係底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我唔係唔識讀書，只不過係唔鍾意大學個種讀書模式，翻學放學都自己一個，搞到我唔鍾意翻去。我仲有5個sem追，我只想要個second up，有無人可以鼓勵吓我，或者鬧吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"85f8b64f3648c398fab153838daccbe5ed5ee288","tid":92714,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:42:02.000Z","msg":"Why don't step out"},{"pid":"3f378808c5fcee8e116622c9e9d5117fa1bd4f83","tid":92714,"uid":75484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:44:18.000Z","msg":"social life是很重要的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0de666d07549488bd1bbb2d38b5d6a36dcdf4f","tid":92714,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:45:29.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎"},{"pid":"fa0e0cb0af05b005572e679f4c0a71265bf552a6","tid":92714,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己攞黎</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5209d92e0d12b7063962c9e242244f2b54d7c043","tid":92714,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Why don't step out</blockquote><br />\n如何，year2了，而且我唔太鍾意social，叫我踢波打波做gym無問題，但叫我social我真係唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cd015f4c4aa3067ae91c562d588b323fc05e4b","tid":92714,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T1